import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container';
import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav';
import Navbar from 'react-bootstrap/Navbar';
import '../App.css'

const HeaderComponent = () => {
    return (
        <Nav className="justify-content-center" activeKey="/home">
        <Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Link href="/home" class = "fs-3 px-2 mt-0 fst-italic Tom">Home</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Link href="/Projects" class = "fs-3 px-2 mt-0 fst-italic Tom">Projects</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Link href="/Contact" class = "fs-3 px-2 mt-0 fst-italic Tom">Contact</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Link href="/About" class = "fs-3 px-2 mt-0 fst-italic Tom">
            About
          </Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
      </Nav>
    )
}

export default HeaderComponent
